</object>
</li>
				<li><a href="get.php?web=casted-yatil-2006-08-04-78947.mp3" title="Amazon Redux und XHTML2">MP3 herunterladen<br />(2.4&nbsp;MB&nbsp;| 6:56&nbsp;min)</a></li>
